    "originContent": "## Features",
    "translatedContent": "## 功能特性"
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "6lwZvb+w//XXHMp+OkdqpC3pRshDk7nwwMoi05AMhzU=",
    "originContent": "- Supports convertion between following formats:",
    "translatedContent": "- 支持以下格式之间的转换："
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "pIY1Q9a9ReetN3zx9CKcTcgcH+rkWV0D5nsXGkSyVoM=",
    "originContent": "    - ISO / XISO",
    "translatedContent": "    - ISO / XISO"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "b2EJYipkbND96uw53IYtGksEJDzSJ0Qf05cNz5pdVxM=",
    "originContent": "    - Extracted files (Xex / Xbe / HDD Ready)",
    "translatedContent": "    - 提取文件（Xex / Xbe / HDD Ready）"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "e4VyGCYB2J+IcIIM/7VWbtSAKl/QrnUr8r88AnJEylQ=",
    "originContent": "    - GoD / Games on Demand",
    "translatedContent": "    - GoD / 按需游戏下载"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "0QcIey44+qnzvHN2Kqg/ByKRQZSkKfijhp2On6OIlqk=",
    "originContent": "    - CCI",
    "translatedContent": "    - CCI"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "52wLIu4/576bhIES3uJiVcGVlR24bX9zwZcIHM3VDfI=",
    "originContent": "    - CSO",
    "translatedContent": "    - CSO"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "F6RGsQ2OyRr63GGXymnEbh5ZNPKWFCB3z7WAtbR4WUA=",
    "originContent": "    - ZAR",
    "translatedContent": "    - ZAR"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "e3ZMbngTI94u9qA55FW9hb812K/KLW4yN/OpD5gF0do=",
    "originContent": "- Seamless conversion, e.g. you can directly extract a GoD image, convert an ISO to ZAR archive, or extracted directory to CCI archive, without writing any temporary files. The only format requiring temporary files is ZAR when provided as input.",
    "translatedContent": "- 无缝转换，例如，您可以直接提取GoD镜像，将ISO转换为ZAR档案，或将提取目录转换为CCI档案，无需写入任何临时文件。唯一需要临时文件的格式是作为输入的ZAR。"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "3IxLBnn2FgRjcwExamcdTlkc1d/E5n5jHSXk2kJnXXo=",
    "originContent": "- Image scrubbing (\"Partial Scrub\"), gets rid of random padding and trims the output file to the shortest length possible.",
    "translatedContent": "- 镜像清理（“部分清理”），去除随机填充并将输出文件修剪到最短长度。"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "GqIbg82SGIDEzp9igGrJpyGB1D8LPpoSO11sYsdwcds=",
    "originContent": "- Image reauthoring (\"Full Scrub\"), completely rewrites the structure of the disc for the smallest possible output file.",
    "translatedContent": "- 镜像重构（“完全清理”），完全重写光盘结构以获得尽可能小的输出文件。"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "x2+lAGRD0xUETPfzbaM/oxSjPyyzrtv+GyRuApq2hTc=",
    "originContent": "- Image authoring, takes your extracted files and creates a new image with them.",
    "translatedContent": "- 镜像制作，使用您的提取文件创建新的镜像。"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "GLrCOrPm4Ivukl7N1AitSJlxB23bjMDwQ+REfppJ1Yg=",
    "originContent": "- Multithreaded compression for CCI and CSO formats.",
    "translatedContent": "- CCI和CSO格式的多线程压缩。"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "CsMVE9VT1Pd5g69oP2aAug0lZ26uY2Bxje7PMAs1gFc=",
    "originContent": "- Batch processing, a folder full of different game formats can be batch converted to a single format.",
    "translatedContent": "- 批量处理，可以将一个文件夹中不同游戏格式批量转换为单一格式。"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "VNo0AH2H5tjrp7SqevucYIfflJvrQWTGsXFO6afGid8=",
    "originContent": "- Automatically finds split files when only one part is provided as an input path, assuming they're named in this format: ```name.1.extension``` ```name.2.extension```.",
    "translatedContent": "- 当仅提供一个部分作为输入路径时，自动查找分割文件，假设文件命名格式为：```name.1.extension``` ```name.2.extension```。"
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "U1E0ciFFGcAjYhBXCpxlrP4i42IB21mZk4LfAiLMVqY=",
    "originContent": "- Option to select your target app/machine (Xemu, Xenia, OG Xbox, Xbox 360) and let XGDTool decide which settings to use.",
    "translatedContent": "- 可选择目标应用/设备（Xemu、Xenia、OG Xbox、Xbox 360），让XGDTool自动决定使用的设置。"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "uIn3CFyW2Tkn5Zwo1oMjKQlfQYgv4H1hxRfGQctv4w8=",
    "originContent": "- Attach XBE generation for OG Xbox.",
    "translatedContent": "- 支持OG Xbox的XBE生成。"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "TFGfM7rpyGumTRn97W3SCbZ7Cel9Wc8nhoE2i21pAHI=",
    "originContent": "- Online database lookup for accurate file naming (can be disabled).",
    "translatedContent": "- 在线数据库查询以获得准确的文件命名（可禁用）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
