    "rowsha": "W20xCCVYWcr5MPa4SDXdi7lFB+yJQRg9mC4bQ6uq1/s=",
    "originContent": "- ```--zar```       Creates a ZAR archive",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--xbe```       生成附加的 XBE 文件，不转换输入文件"
