    "rowsha": "TK4y2vHXr68MixBs1drTyafay8W4GUZAzc5gJoXHtVo=",
    "originContent": "- ```--ogxbox```    Automatically choose format and settings for use with OG Xbox",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--xbox360```   自动选择格式和设置以用于 Xbox 360"
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "+RYmt+BPxxjH5pm1XLJLLInU0Fq1i4eiBClmV+WCvRQ=",
    "originContent": "- ```--xbox360```   Automatically choose format and settings for use with Xbox 360",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--xemu```      自动选择格式和设置以用于 Xemu"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "SsPnGMhO5hmcDG33gzLvPq4X6gIobc4T1t6vU8J3ZBk=",
