    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### 设置标志"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "3RjiuoWJPCB2NhHj29zolz7hJNKgmXOpFdYPm3EWUok=",
    "originContent": "### Settings flags",
    "translatedContent": "这些参数可以叠加使用，尽管不是所有输出格式都会使用它们，在那种情况下该选项会被忽略。如果提供了冲突的设置（例如全擦除/部分擦除），将使用最后一个设置。"
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "2+w+ffIUVQsBUdI1JfxTVjQDBq5COjLfF6RrEadpXdg=",
    "originContent": "These arguments can be stacked, though not all output formats will use them, in that case the option is ignored. If any conflicting settings are provided (e.g. full/partial scrub), the last one will be used. ",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--partial-scrub```  擦除并修剪输出镜像，移除随机填充数据。"
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "bqC+QmbDyzuy/Rnk/a1ye49Z4XJyZ9/1sQreGJGfSBc=",
    "originContent": "- ```--partial-scrub```  Scrubs and trims the output image, random padding data is removed.",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--full-scrub```     完全重新制作生成的镜像，这将产生尽可能小的文件。"
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "p0NkrDFUBKq+6Il15nrX4SwOXcrrj1GtUWGO3lXuQNY=",
    "originContent": "- ```--full-scrub```     Completely reauthor the resulting image, this will produce the smallest file possible.",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--split```          如果生成的 XISO 文件对原版 Xbox 过大，则拆分它。"
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "OVeVfN7kKmA9yVIhBnF/J8jxBRYHdN433E6mRs+xmUY=",
    "originContent": "- ```--split```          Splits the resulting XISO file if it's too large for OG Xbox.",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--rename```         修补生成的 XBE 文件的标题字段为数据库中找到的名称。"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "FLOUI3YiQhIKWPZ1MLYmpXn5NriqHL/bx2fHtR/4Z78=",
    "originContent": "- ```--rename```         Patches the title field of resulting XBE files to one found in the database.",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--attach-xbe```     生成一个附加的 XBE 文件与输出文件一起。"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "Sg1chdMU7WptARbz9WHiuuP0S1xON7gwGurhdjRfgrM=",
    "originContent": "- ```--attach-xbe```     Generates an attach XBE file along with the output file.",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--am-patch```       修补生成的 XBE 文件中的“允许媒体”字段。"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "aWUYIlkidZziLI9MO1/bjpRtrSmY7bZxxV6vaXQ1+MY=",
    "originContent": "- ```--am-patch```       Patches the \"Allowed Media\" field in resulting XBE files.",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--offline```        禁用在线功能。"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "Jwfe2lsG3F5VWfhKnVP+jWeuVYKoTYJUQaklZwLJm0I=",
    "originContent": "- ```--offline```        Disables online functionality.",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--debug```          启用调试日志。"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "29xCaxLZ4AfPrdLavYNAz585mZYUnuy/fSAbOuSAQhs=",
    "originContent": "- ```--debug```          Enable debug logging.",
    "translatedContent": "- ```--quiet```          禁用除警告和错误之外的所有日志。"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "sd65A6loHvwbWWYiMEX31U8fzlTbCbIRIfWG5b5TRHw=",
    "originContent": "- ```--quiet```          Disable all logging except for warnings and errors.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 构建"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "sJ/yPrjOl4CqqmNX52jV/O9t1ocQUKu6R6aB9zUAdQM=",
    "originContent": "## Build",
    "translatedContent": "默认情况下，此项目编译为 GUI，使用 Cmake 配置时加上 ```-DENABLE_GUI=OFF``` 可编译为 CLI。要编译为 x86，需要对 CmakeLists.txt 和 cmake/setup_vcpkg.cmake 文件做一些更改以适应。"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "KCF0MpStobKVwF2vjLK9fdRAv52jy7ju6cQ+Lwgw69k=",
    "originContent": "By default this compiles as a GUI, configure Cmake with ```-DENABLE_GUI=OFF``` to compile for CLI. To compile for x86 there would need to be several changes made to the CmakeLists.txt and cmake/seutp_vcpkg.cmake files to accound for that.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### Windows"
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "0FiuH2W03qY+Bo6hltZlihXJBluFMyZj/iTpeAXb4Xk=",
    "originContent": "### Windows",
    "translatedContent": "如果你安装了 Cmake 和 MSVC，流程应该相当简单。该项目已为 Windows 设置，配置 Cmake 后会自动下载并使用 vcpkg 在项目目录内构建所有依赖项。根据你的网络速度和电脑性能，这可能需要一些时间，但只需执行一次。"
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "Tbln4WJtDGPFgArk+n2VMMvlH9Ebjr7QBMMXD9ZWJgM=",
    "originContent": "If you have Cmake and MSVC installed, things should be fairly simple. The project has been setup for Windows so that it will automatically download and build all dependancies with vcpkg inside the project directory by configuring with Cmake. This can take a while depending on your internet speeds and PC specs but only has to happen once.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "克隆此仓库并创建一个构建目录"
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "Y/3Tbc2DoKRz+zyLfmLoA6MqCZ33L/Dg6vnFn1k2sFk=",
    "originContent": "Clone this repo and make a build directory",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
